    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-07-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-07-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="129" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d129">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Adams</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1230.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,
                                        <hi rend="italic">London,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-07-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 7, 1866</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have received a telegraphic despatch
                            from Mr. West, the consult Dublin, communicating the information that
                            Colonel Burke and Daniel <pb facs="0221" n="147" xml:id="pg_147"/>
                            Mykins had been liberated. I regret to learn also that the reply in the
                            ease of Hynes is very unfavorable. Mr. West promises a full report in a
                            despatch by the post on Monday. But as that will be too late for the bag
                            this week, I thought it best to communicate the substance of his report
                            to you at once.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>CHARLES FRANCIS ADAMS.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
